Package: usbguardgui
Version: 1.0.0
Maintainer: Bigyls
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: usbguard, python3, python3-dbus, python3-gi, zenity
Homepage: https://github.com/Bigyls/USBGuardGUI
Description: Popup for Allow/Deny USB with USBGuard
  As soon as you connect a USB device to your PC,
  the tool will display a popup
  and add an authorization rule to USBGuard
  if you allow the USB
